Brainchild of director Kate Champion and associate artist Kelli Jean Drinkwater, it will run at the Malthouse Theatre in Melbourne, Australia.

The company's artistic director, Kate, teamed up with filmmaker and activist recognised internationally for her work in radical body politics, Kelli, in order to explore and celebrate the movement of bigger bodies in the show.

