Speaking about the production, Kelli said: 'When Kate told me she wanted to create a new piece of dance theatre with a cast of undeniably bigger bodies I was overwhelmed.

'But the response to Nothing to Lose has been positive beyond our wildest expectations.

'We've had huge amounts of interest internationally - from places as far and wide as London to Hong Kong to Buenos Aires.

'It has been overwhelming and also validating to realise that this subject really speaks to people.' 

